# Environment documentation for the __CSD_TITLE__ walkthrough. Copy the vars you
# need into each app's local env (.env.local) or its Vercel project. The full
# per-project matrix (which var goes on WHICH Vercel project) is docs/deploy.md.

# --- Zone URLs (set on the TOUR/SHELL project only; read at BUILD time) -------
# One per zone app, named __CSD_ENV_PREFIX___<APPSLUG>_ZONE_URL, e.g.:
# __CSD_ENV_PREFIX___VAULT_ZONE_URL=https://your-vault-deployment.example

# --- Pod-guard rail (each app with authenticated pod routes; fails closed) ----
__CSD_ENV_PREFIX___TRUSTED_OIDC_ISSUERS=
__CSD_ENV_PREFIX___POD_ALLOWED_ORIGINS=
# Behind a TLS-terminating proxy (Vercel) the forwarded host is authoritative:
# __CSD_ENV_PREFIX___TRUST_FORWARDED_HEADERS=1
# Local dev/e2e ONLY (loopback HTTP issuer + in-memory pods); never in production:
# __CSD_ENV_PREFIX___DEV_ALLOW_LOOPBACK=1

# --- Seed target (pnpm run seed writes the demo persona here) -----------------
__CSD_ENV_PREFIX___SEED_POD_URL=
__CSD_ENV_PREFIX___SEED_WEBID=
